snippet.title: dxjx23
snippet.description: My job is to show you the door, you are the one who has to walk through it. Many topics and different things all around the world. A journey through science, religion, racism and many other things that the world is mixed up in. All of us hold a key and we must work together so that door opens. The truth is never easy to accept but by keeping an open mind, free it from the hold Satan has on it and use common sense. Do your research, leave no stone lying on the ground and eventually you will find the answer. Everything cannot be explained but we can try to solve the easiest ones most people seem to have issues with.
